    </div>
    <div class="flex ">
        <div class="flex-row justify-items-center mx-auto px-8 basis-1/2">
            <Card title='How we first met!' body="It was Christmas time and we both found ourselves at Bloomingdale\'s trying to puchase the same \
                    pair of black cashmere gloves. We basically fell in love instantly, but Kristen decided to leave our entire potential relationship up to fate. \
