        </div>




        <div class="flex-row justify-items-center mx-auto px-8 basis-1/2">
            <Card title='Last night out before Covid' body="Honestly, the fact that Kristen and I found each out just a few months before Covid hit was so \
                        fortunate, but it also had its own challenges. One example is the fact that we really couldn't do any more 'out on the town' \
